title: Rangers in playoffs, near AL West title after edging Angels
text:
> Texas Rangers in playoffs, near AL West title after edging Angels Los Angeles Angels' Albert Pujols rounds the bases on his way home after hitting a solo home run off a pitch from Texas Rangers' Derek Holland in the sixth inning of a baseball game Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015, in Arlington, Texas.
